HEADWORD: Reliquary
<hw>Rel"i*qua*ry</hw> <pr>(r?l"?-kw?-r?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>;
<plu><it>pl.</it> <plw>-ries</plw> <pr>(-r⟦icr⟧z)</pr>.</plu> <ety>[LL.
